First invocation (2026-07-14): fail before assertions completed.

Cause:
The zsh special variable `path` was used as a loop variable. This replaced the shell PATH array, so a later `rg` invocation failed with:
zsh:18: command not found: rg

Correction:
The loop variable was renamed to `repo_path`; no research content was changed to mask the command error.

